---
title: Spicy Miso Rigatoni With Bacon plus Caramelized Shallot, Zucchini & Parmesan
description: Bacon makes everything better! It boosts other umami-rich ingredients like miso and Parmesan for this irresistible fusion dish. The bacon joins zucchini and shallot in a savory sauce flavored with garlic and Sriracha and swirled with butter and sour cream for a luxuriously creamy pasta bowl that’s sure to be an instant hit—all in just 30 minutes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66f2d7231e86f3e65846f9ef-14b62af8.jpeg
